@token = {{$dotenv TOKEN}}  

### Auth - get a fresh token
POST http://localhost:4000/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "username": "{{$dotenv AUTH_USERNAME}}",
    "password": "{{$dotenv AUTH_PASSWORD}}"
}

###

### Post a reading
POST http://localhost:4000/readings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "sensor_id": "living-room",
    "temperature": 21.5,
    "humidity": 63.2,
    "air_quality": 142
}

###

### Get all readings
GET http://localhost:4000/readings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get AI compliance report
GET http://localhost:4000/compliance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get living-room compliance
GET http://localhost:4000/compliance/living-room
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
